      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new? I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014she is in stunning, mint condition! Seriously, it looks and smells like it just left the dealership. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so there isn\u2019t a single scratch or hiccup to be found. It\u2019s super smooth to drive and totally ready for its next adventure. I'd love for you to come by, see it in person, and take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to fall in love! Feel free to reach out with any questions at all!",
