    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional E46 M3, featuring the naturally aspirated S54B32 inline-six engine. This high-compression power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver a seamless power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. This specimen has been meticulously maintained with a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, mitigating common platform vulnerabilities. The chassis remains taut, benefitting from refreshed bushings and an OEM-spec suspension that preserves the communicative steering rack and 50/50 weight distribution. Presented in flawless condition with a documented service history, this is a definitive example for the purist collector.",
      "price": 46500.0,
